        "\n",
        "def run_subprocess_command(cmd):\n",
        "    # run the command\n",
        "    process = subprocess.Popen(cmd.split(), stdout=subprocess.PIPE)\n",
        "    # print the output\n",
        "    for line in process.stdout:\n",
        "        print(line.decode().strip())\n",
